  "remarks": "JSC Tupolev a Russian military industry company. It supplies warplanes to the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation. It has developed the Tu-160 strategic missile carriers and TU-22M3M/TU-22M3 long-range bombers, which are manufactured by its subsidiary company, Kazan Aircraft Production Association. The Tu-160 and the TU-22M3M/TU-22M3 are used by the Russian Air Force in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
